{"tid":2070822,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗3M面罩，大家其實仲有更加好嘅選擇 vol.6","createTime":"2020-06-19T11:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T17:52:07.000Z","uid":254456,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d852f4c357d62247b23418576eebbf5103b2b8b4","tid":2070822,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"<em>以下文章由 薛丁格的豬 巴打 ( #10133 ) 撰寫<br />\n以及由 蛋撻哥哥 巴打 ( #254456 ) 修訂</em><br />\n<br />\n其實除左3M 面罩同濾罐，大家仲有更好嘅選擇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487835\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487835</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗3M面罩，大家其實仲有更加好嘅選擇 vol.2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553966\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553966</a><br />\n<br />\n除左3m面罩 其實有啲更好仲平仲好用vol3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663077\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663077</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗3M面罩，大家其實仲有更加好嘅選擇 vol.4<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1841354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1841354</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗3M面罩，大家其實仲有更加好嘅選擇 vol.5<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892801/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892801/</a><br />\n<br />\n面罩嘅防護level<br />\n<br />\n由<span style=\"color: green;\">N95</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqEE8Oa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqEE8Oa.jpg&h=9e575337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ( 3M 8210 ) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Half Face</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wd1cKmB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWd1cKmB.png&h=42dbb835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ( 3M 6200 ) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Full Face </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTX7ye7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTX7ye7.png&h=b92a0963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ( 3M 6800 )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">PAPR</span> ( 通常係醫護使用 ) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjZxKmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjZxKmS.jpg&h=f732b251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ( 3M TR-300 ) <br />\n<br />\n去到<span style=\"color: navy;\">內循環式</span>（ 好似潛水咁款 ）<br />\n<br />\nN95 其實幫到你阻隔咗一啲刺激物<br />\n唔好再用外科口罩<br />\n除左遮樣一啲用都無<br />\n<br />\nN95 係one size fits all <br />\n唔一定Fit 你面形<br />\n但正確使用可以令你係Tear gas 下無咁辛苦。<br />\n ( 一樣會照食到 ) <br />\n<br />\n接住就係3M Half Face Mask<br />\n缺點有三個<br />\n<br />\n- 無護眼<br />\n<br />\n- Filter 唔防水<br />\n<br />\n- 配件過多<br />\n<br />\n眼你可以買多個泳鏡戴<br />\n解決其中一個問題<br />\n<br />\n但P100 暴露在外<br />\n一濕水防護力就會大大減低<br />\n<br />\n3M Full Face 講緊最少$1000 起跳<br />\n市面有$400左右的大陸開心版<br />\n但開心版氣密有機會出來問題<br />\n仲有上面嘅缺點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">平時無Tear gas 請唔好戴住豬咀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為你消耗緊濾網嘅壽命<br />\n遮樣請用返面巾<br />\n<br />\n長期喺阻力之下呼吸<br />\n呼吸相關嘅肌肉<br />\n例如橫膈膜<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有機會發炎</span><br />\n_____________________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個好嘅防毒面具最緊要係氣密</span><br />\n<br />\n當你戴好Gas Mask 後<br />\n應該用手㩒住吸氣位再吸氣<br />\n確保冇空氣會在入到去<br />\n<br />\n只要佢氣密<br />\n佢就係一個好嘅防毒面具<br />\n<br />\n6200係比人哋工業 / 化學用<br />\n唔係俾你打架用<br />\n<br />\n_____________________________<br />\n<br />\n網絡上充斥着好多唔同時期 / 唔同品牌嘅防毒面具<br />\n應該點選擇呢？<br />\n<br />\n一個稱職嘅軍用防毒面具<br />\n除咗要氣密<br />\n仲可能會有<br />\n<br />\n- 飲水管<br />\n<br />\n- 通話器<br />\netc.<br />\n<br />\n飲水管其實比較多餘<br />\n因為你要配合特定嘅水樽蓋<br />\n<br />\n另外通話器其實就係一張膠膜<br />\n令到喺面具入邊嘅你<br />\n講嘅說話可以清晰傳遞<br />\n其他人亦都可以聽到你嘅說話<br />\n<br />\n全罩式防毒面具<br />\n一般有五 / 六個索帶 ( 有部分面具係用網 ) 去固定<br />\n<br />\n半罩式防毒面具嘅索帶就好容易走位<br />\n俾敵人一扯就甩<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具嘅使用方式非常簡單<br />\n就算敵人射咗催淚彈你臨急臨忙先砌<br />\n因為得兩個部件<br />\n受訓練後係10秒內（ 閉氣 ）都可以deploy 到<br />\n<br />\n<em> 以下由 插爛花 ( #188111 ) 巴打 提供 </em><br />\n<blockquote><strong>平價之選 可對摺 Filter置中 ~$200-500</strong><br />\n4a1 （多數新淨 兩用Thread 有用家反映會起霧 視野偏窄 Amazon都有）<br />\nM65 （Nato)<br />\n（下面係抄M65出嘅 多數仲平 同新啲）<br />\nRomanian M74/M85 (Nato)<br />\nCm4 (兩用Thread )<br />\nBulgarian PG-1 （youtube話GOST thread 但上網見到話係兩用 TBC）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>貴少少之選~$500-$900</strong><br />\nM95(Nato Filter上左右邊）<br />\nM15 (兩用Thread Filter置中 Amazon都有)<br />\nForsheda A4 (Forsheda F2民用版 Nato Thread 舒適度高）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>平價panoramic~$300-600</strong><br />\nMP5 (Nato Filter置中）<br />\nBEM-4GP （Nato 隨時改變Filter左中右位置 留意飲水位易爛）<br />\n4301m (新版PPM88 兩用Thread; <strong>感謝 超型meme囝 巴打 ( #76413 ) 提供資料</strong> ) <br />\n<br />\n<strong>工業用(Nato/En148 Thread ~$400-600) </strong><br />\nClimax 731/732 <br />\nSpasciani  TR2002<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">價格只供參考 但全部1000蚊內搞掂 可以係ebay或者ebay uk搵到 總有一款你啱用</span></strong><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fee2301055515053c6ff31ba0eb86a682531f91a","tid":2070822,"uid":254456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好用蘇聯時期嘅濾罐</span><br />\n<br />\n絕大多數嘅蘇聯時期防毒面具嘅原裝濾罐<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">證實含有石棉</span><br />\n一旦吸入石棉<br />\n佢就會永遠卡住喺你個肺<br />\n可致癌及塵肺病 ( 正宗頂你個肺 ) <br />\n如果你用緊蘇聯時期嘅原裝濾罐<br />\n請你立即停止使用該濾罐<br />\n並且小心棄置千萬不要拆開<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇聯時期嘅面具<br />\n只要配合近代嘅濾罐<br />\n使用風險不大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjQQtGu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjQQtGu.jpg&h=a97d9acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">不要</span>使用GP5/7 的原裝濾罐<br />\n________________________<br />\n當你有一個氣密功能好好嘅面罩<br />\n你就需要一個真正過濾到刺激物嘅濾罐<br />\n<br />\n濾罐方面我地需要NBC ( 有啲會寫CBRN )<br />\nNBC stands for <br />\n- Nuclear<br />\n<br />\n- Biological<br />\n<br />\n- Chemical<br />\n<br />\n無錯，乜都防到<br />\n<br />\n一般軍用防毒規格都係NATO 40mm ( 蘇聯時期則多數使用GOST 40mm ) <br />\n<br />\n濾罐會有使用期限<br />\n網上購買嘅濾罐好多都係過期<br />\n甚至係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有致癌石棉嘅蘇聯時期濾罐</span><br />\n<br />\n濾罐嘅使用期限會影響到佢嘅作用<br />\n例如用嚟痴過濾紙嘅膠水可能會隨時間而分解<br />\n過濾碳亦都可以因為保養不佳而失去效力<br />\n但如果濾罐有良好嘅儲存環境（ 密封 )<br />\n即是過期數年都可以正常使用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前提係不要蘇聯時期<br />\n非常重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">注意NBC濾罐可能會被扣起</span><br />\n因為中咗戰略物品管制條例 ( 1a004 ) <br />\n請自行承擔風險<br />\n<br />\n詳細請參閱 : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.stc.tid.gov.hk/service/productSearchAction.do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stc.tid.gov.hk%2Fservice%2FproductSearchAction.do&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=f0cc3844\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.stc.tid.gov.hk/service/productSearchAction.do</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你害怕濾罐不能過關<br />\n你可以轉買Scott Pro2000 工業用濾罐<br />\n工業用filter 會有3個Rating，例如ABEK2P3<br />\n就會勁過ABEK1P1。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZapx2U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZapx2U.png&h=6d59fb5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nScott Pro<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2</span>000"},{"pid":"9e8e035c3d823eb3fc9dad00b1476d88131a0135","tid":2070822,"uid":254456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n有啲手足可能要戴眼鏡先至睇得清楚<br />\n但係又唔想用隱形眼鏡<br />\n喺呢一個時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">MAG 1</span></span>就會幫到你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFCMcQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFCMcQQ.jpg&h=5ddfe685&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面係可以用MAG 1嘅防毒面具列表<br />\n<em>資訊來自TG Channel 龍珠抗疫大法 </em><br />\n<blockquote>由於每個星期都有人問自己隻mask用唔用到mag-1，所以直接整理一個list比大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n用到： <br />\n<br />\nAvon S10<br />\nAvon C50/M50<br />\nScott GSR/FRR<br />\nMSA Millennium<br />\nM40<br />\nSGE series<br />\nPromask<br />\nCM6 series<br />\nOM90(CM7M)<br />\nM15<br />\n4A1<br />\nMaskpol MP5/French AFR-A<br />\nFMJ05<br />\nPPM88<br />\n3M 7800<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人用到有人用唔到：<br />\n<br />\nAvon FM12<br />\nForsheda A4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用唔到：<br />\nM95<br />\nGP5<br />\n <br />\n如果有錯/有漏，歡迎pm我更正，所以呢份名單會不斷更新。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e432ca761f63e0e6228c8f9192c3ce4ce44c926c","tid":2070822,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"前一個post嘅精選留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>宇智波月巴 ( #136590 ) </em><br />\n<blockquote>又平又實用嘅話我會揀Israeli 4a1<br />\nebay長期有貨 amazon我記得有一排都有賣 但係依家好似冇咗<br />\n啱啱喺ebay睇$500樓下就買到 連埋運費同filter嘅話$700 budget應該點都搞得掂<br />\n當然舒適度就一定冇貴價mask咁好<br />\n<br />\n如果夠錢買貴少少嘅話 可以諗下以下幾款<br />\n1.) Israeli M15 (有個voice diaphragm講嘢清楚啲 ebay賣around $700)<br />\n2.) Scott M95 (整體設計好 ebay賣around $700)<br />\n3.) MP-5 (視野夠闊 ebay賣around $700)<br />\n4.) Forsheda f2a4 (設計同s10差唔多 但係比s10平一截 ebay賣around $800)<br />\n<br />\n本來S10其實幾值得推薦<br />\n但係由6月開始個價位就係咁升 我諗升咗兩倍都有<br />\n依家起碼$1200先買到一個 完全唔撚值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nebay $1200 budget已經買到FM12 咁嘅話根本冇必要考慮s10<br />\n<br />\n再貴啲嘅話 仲有FM12,C4,C50,GSR,MSA Millennium呢堆<br />\n如果想要最頂級嘅話就直接入FM53 不過真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>宇智波月巴 ( #136590 ) </em><br />\n<blockquote>s10原裝filter係將chromium同活性碳溝埋一齊做particulate filter layer<br />\n只要你見唔到有活性碳漏出嚟 咁即係啲chromium都會同樣困住咗出唔到嚟 基本上係可以放心用<br />\n下面條片係一個最簡單檢查filter有冇爛到嘅方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mMJKbleMuHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmMJKbleMuHY&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=640f5b49\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mMJKbleMuHY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於致癌嘅問題 曾經有美國研究掂過呢個topic<br />\n佢地嘅結論係你要日日戴 戴足30-40年 先會有高1-2%嘅機率生cancer<br />\n咁其實隨時食多兩條腸仔都易生cancer過戴chromium filter<br />\n詳細可以睇埋下面條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A9I7L2534fM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA9I7L2534fM&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=a647bc4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A9I7L2534fM</a><br />\n<br />\n當然如果你真係好唔放心 或者 個filter過咗期好耐<br />\n咁就唔好搏 買過個新嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>宇智波月巴 ( #136590 ) </em><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.stc.tid.gov.hk/service/productSearch.do?locale=chi&amp;text=0[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stc.tid.gov.hk%2Fservice%2FproductSearch.do%3Flocale%3Dchi%26text%3D0%5B%2Furl%5D&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=e39abae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stc.tid.gov.hk/service/productSearch.do?locale=chi&amp;text=0[/url]</a><br />\ncheck晒mp5 fp5 maskpol 都冇話係受管制<br />\n照計就應該冇問題 可以安全運到入嚟<br />\n<br />\n但係佢未必每一樣受管制嘅物品都會寫晒上網<br />\n如果見到fit 1A004A嘅嘢 佢都可能會照扣起<br />\n當然依家咁多手足都有full face 證明呢個風險都係偏低<br />\n不過安全起見 我都係極極極極強烈建議大家唔好揀直送上門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>宇智波月巴 ( #136590 ) </em><br />\n<blockquote>我上面講得唔好<br />\nabekp多數係工業用filter嘅標準<br />\ncbrn/nbc就通常係軍用filter嘅標準<br />\n但係有某啲軍用filter都會寫埋abekp同埋每一種chemical擋到幾耐<br />\n不過應該得好少filter會咁寫<br />\n<br />\n我話認住&quot;ABEK1P3&quot;係因為工業用filter係最易揾<br />\n而且你肯定買到未過期嘅 同埋貨源充足<br />\n軍用唔係難揾 但係要揾肯定係未過期嘅就有難度</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c76f0f9ea2887fd8c64057ce88ca50a9c251cef9","tid":2070822,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整合得好，加番句之前有人講FP5 可以兼容NATO 同GOST mask其實係weaponandstuff信左流料講嘅<br />\n<br />\n事實係FP5係跟NATO standard 造，有啲GOST mask 上到係因為GOST mask 嘅生產有誤差，導致啲紋有時fit 到"},{"pid":"10787fc29e4604daeb565f8de8a96a370e1a59f0","tid":2070822,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"買A2B2E2K2 P3 保全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個四人家庭最少 六隻full face mask (CBRN rated)<br />\n加12 個未過期嘅CBRN 罐，可自行選購P3, Half face mask 作防疫用<br />\n<br />\n算式：N = 人數 <br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN Full Face Mask u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n1.5 N<br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN filters (not expired) u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n3 N<br />\n<br />\n加埋常規配戴同換罐訓練 <br />\n<br />\n意外火燭都可以頂到 <br />\n<br />\n呢排世界唔好<br />\n<br />\n天氣不似預期 生命無價"},{"pid":"f754e11a83963b085af9d83af823cb48c2e4de71","tid":2070822,"uid":77034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10787fc29e4604daeb565f8de8a96a370e1a59f0","tid":2070822,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"買A2B2E2K2 P3 保全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個四人家庭最少 六隻full face mask (CBRN rated)<br />\n加12 個未過期嘅CBRN 罐，可自行選購P3, Half face mask 作防疫用<br />\n<br />\n算式：N = 人數 <br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN Full Face Mask u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n1.5 N<br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN filters (not expired) u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n3 N<br />\n<br />\n加埋常規配戴同換罐訓練 <br />\n<br />\n意外火燭都可以頂到 <br />\n<br />\n呢排世界唔好<br />\n<br />\n天氣不似預期 生命無價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:30:51.000Z","msg":"有錢真係買定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927de71602a4d49ef262c0d54acb3306de796b5c","tid":2070822,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10787fc29e4604daeb565f8de8a96a370e1a59f0","tid":2070822,"uid":41974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"買A2B2E2K2 P3 保全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個四人家庭最少 六隻full face mask (CBRN rated)<br />\n加12 個未過期嘅CBRN 罐，可自行選購P3, Half face mask 作防疫用<br />\n<br />\n算式：N = 人數 <br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN Full Face Mask u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n1.5 N<br />\n<br />\n# of CBRN filters (not expired) u should keep in home<br />\n<br />\n3 N<br />\n<br />\n加埋常規配戴同換罐訓練 <br />\n<br />\n意外火燭都可以頂到 <br />\n<br />\n呢排世界唔好<br />\n<br />\n天氣不似預期 生命無價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T20:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c2684c